---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="IT Consulting Brisbane"
  page="services"
  description="Aurora ICT provides IT consulting in Brisbane with IT consultant and virtual CTO support to reduce risk, simplify systems and vendors, and build practical technology roadmaps."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">IT Consulting Brisbane for Growing Businesses</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Aurora ICT provides IT consulting in Brisbane and across South East Queensland for businesses that need clearer technology direction, better risk control, and simpler systems and vendor management. If you are comparing broader non-location-specific advisory support, see our <a href="/it-consulting" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">general IT consulting page</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Whether you need targeted IT consultant support or ongoing virtual CTO guidance, this Brisbane page is designed as a local advisory overview with practical outcomes your leadership team can use immediately.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
            style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);"
          >
            Book a free initial consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/services"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white"
          >
            Explore services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">What Aurora ICT helps with</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>technology strategy and prioritisation linked to business outcomes</li>
          <li>digital roadmaps with practical 90-day and 12-month next steps</li>
          <li>cyber risk reduction and clearer security governance</li>
          <li>simpler systems, tools, and vendor management</li>
          <li>virtual CTO support for leadership oversight and decision quality</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Who this is for</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>growing businesses that have outgrown ad hoc IT decisions</li>
          <li>teams managing multiple tools and vendors without clear ownership</li>
          <li>leaders needing strategic IT guidance without a full-time CTO</li>
          <li>organisations in Brisbane and South East Queensland planning their next growth stage</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Key outcomes</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>reduced technology waste and avoidable spend</li>
          <li>lower cyber and operational risk exposure</li>
          <li>clearer technology decisions and delivery accountability</li>
          <li>roadmaps that support scale with less complexity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Why Aurora ICT</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Aurora ICT combines strategic advisory depth with practical execution support. Our Brisbane IT consulting engagements are vendor-neutral, business-focused, and designed for growing companies that need clarity before committing larger budgets.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Many clients begin with a <a href="/technology-health-check" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Technology Health Check</a> or a structured <a href="/it-strategy-roadmap" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">digital roadmap</a>, then extend into ongoing virtual CTO support as needed. You can also review the full <a href="/services" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">services hub</a> before choosing the right engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Ready to simplify technology and reduce risk?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Book a free initial consultation to discuss your priorities and the most practical next step for your business, or <a href="/contact" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">contact Aurora ICT</a> with your current priorities.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
            style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);"
          >
            Book a free initial consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/services"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white"
          >
            View all services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
